➜万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 图赏：老派绅士和数码极客的折中之选
https://www.ifanr.com/1380708?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	38673
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380730" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sdfwe.jpg" alt="" width="5679" height="3194" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sdfwe.jpg 5679w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sdfwe-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sdfwe-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/sdfwe-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5679px) 100vw, 5679px" /></p>
<p>传统燃油车品牌转型做新能源，在 2020 年已经不鲜见了。但转型做智能手表的传统腕表厂商，似乎依然屈指可数。</p>
<p>其中，万宝龙算是一个「积极分子」。在 2015 年便推出了「智能表带」，2017 年推出了第一代智能智能腕表 SUMMIT。不过第一代 SUMMIT 的外形实在平平无奇，俗话说就是「没万宝龙那味儿」。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-804861" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/montblanc-summit-smart-watch-2.jpg" alt="万宝龙" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/montblanc-summit-smart-watch-2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/montblanc-summit-smart-watch-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/montblanc-summit-smart-watch-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/montblanc-summit-smart-watch-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 第一代 SUMMIT. 图片来自：<a href="https://hypebeast.com/2017/3/montblanc-summit-smart-watch">Hypebeast</a></p>
</div>
<p>于是万宝龙在 2018 年紧接着发布了 SUMMIT 2，与自家经典的 1858 系列腕表采用了相似的设计语言，象征着它开始「悟了」。我们此前写过<a href="https://www.ifanr.com/1271143">该产品的上手体验</a>，有兴趣的话可以点击阅读。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1271176" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MONTBLANC-Smart-Watch-11.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MONTBLANC-Smart-Watch-11.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MONTBLANC-Smart-Watch-11-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MONTBLANC-Smart-Watch-11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/MONTBLANC-Smart-Watch-11-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 万宝龙 SUMMIT 2</p>
</div>
<p>时隔两年后，SUMMIT 2 迎来了更新，不过升级款不叫 SUMMIT 3，而是叫 SUMMIT 2+。SUMMIT 2+ 共有四个版本，有黑色精钢、青铜色精钢、原色精钢以及女士款（玫瑰金色），表带有皮革款和橡胶款可供选择。我拿到的是原色精钢皮革款。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380709" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07783.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07783.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07783-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07783-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07783-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>乍眼看上去，SUMMIT 2+ 似乎和上一代长得一样。同样精致的外壳，抛光、打磨的工艺和 SUMMIT 2 如出一辙。但仔细看的话，还是很容易找到两者的区别。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380710" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07854.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07854.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07854-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07854-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07854-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>从正脸看，表盘外圈的信息更为丰富了，每隔十分钟的位置都会用数字标注。在正上方加上了万宝龙的品牌名称，使品牌属性得到进一步强化。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380711" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07863.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07863.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07863-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07863-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07863-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>上一代表盘的直径是 42mm，而这一代增大至 43.5mm。AMOLED 显示屏面积也从 1.2 英寸升级至 1.3 英寸，观感上更舒适一些。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380712" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07860.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07860.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07860-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07860-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07860-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>另外一个显眼的变化则是表冠。表冠实际上是一个非常能凸显腕表精致感的组件，然而许多智能手表在表冠上并未下太多功夫。万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 的表冠，也比上一代更大、更有辨识度了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380713" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07858.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07858.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07858-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07858-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07858-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>从侧面看的话，万宝龙黑白相间的 Logo 被印在了表冠的顶端，外圈的设计依旧是 1858 系列的味道。轻按表冠的顶端，可以呼出菜单页面，长按就呼出语音助手。旋转表冠可以滑动菜单，配合几近原生的谷歌 Wear OS，交互上十分顺滑。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380714" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07840.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07840.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07840-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07840-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07840-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>毕竟有传统腕表的设计、生产经验，万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 在按键的交互反馈上做的相当出色。表冠按压的过程是两段式的，第一段是防止误触设计的缓冲层，第二段才能呼出相应的功能。按压的力度不用很大，反馈柔和且干脆。旋转表冠时的阻尼感也比较顺手，不会松垮，也不会过紧。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380715" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07817.jpg" alt="" width="4504" height="3003" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07817.jpg 4504w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07817-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07817-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07817-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4504px) 100vw, 4504px" /></p>
<p>表冠两侧的功能键，也相比上一代更大了。两个功能键都可以自定义，比如我设置的是按压上键呼出简要菜单，按压下键唤出跑步教练。另外，按键反馈的力度同样优秀，清脆不软塌。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380716" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07813.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07813.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07813-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07813-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07813-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>值得一提的是，SUMMIT 2+ 的重量由前代的 132.4 克减轻到 93.6 克，佩戴舒适度上得到了提升。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380717" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07798.jpg" alt="" width="4434" height="2956" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07798.jpg 4434w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07798-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07798-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07798-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4434px) 100vw, 4434px" /></p>
<p>除了外观、重量上的变化，SUMMIT 2+ 和上一代最大的不同，就是新增了 eSIM 功能。用户可以为 SUMMIT 2+ 开通与手机相同或独立的电话号码，通过内置的中国联通 eSIM 卡就可以实现独立通话、连接网络等功能。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380718" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07850.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07850.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07850-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07850-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07850-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>在功能方面，万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 主打健康、户外和商务。其内置的虚拟健身助手，可以根据用户的身高、体重、年龄等信息，来推荐个性化的锻炼计划。可以监测室内外跑步、健走、室外骑行、自由训练几种运动模式。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380719" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07837.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07837.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07837-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07837-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07837-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 的户外功能比较丰富。内置速度计、测高仪、气压计、指南针以及 GPS 全球定位系统，适合经常出门旅行或者喜爱户外运动的用户。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380720" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07865.jpg" alt="" width="2886" height="4329" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07865.jpg 2886w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07865-360x540.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07865-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07865-683x1024.jpg 683w" sizes="(max-width: 2886px) 100vw, 2886px" /></p>
<p>其最有特色的功能当属「Timeshifter」应用。它会基于使用者的睡眠模式、睡眠类型及飞行计划，提供个性化建议，帮助旅行者更快适应新时区。内置的「旅行信息」应用，可以提供多个国家或地区的信息服务，比如重要的信息单词或短语、货币及小费等等。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380721" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07849.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07849.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07849-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07849-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07849-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>另外，万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 还内置了谷歌翻译应用，只需要按住话筒的图标，说出要翻译的内容，该应用就会自动翻译成目标语言，非常适合经常出差异国的商务人士。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380722" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07847.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07847.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07847-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07847-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07847-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>在兼容性上，SUMMIT 2+ 在 iOS 端或 Android 端都可以很好地配对，暂未发现有功能阉割的情况。像 iPhone 端收到的微信、微博、信息等通知，都会同步显示到手表上。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380723" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07835.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07835.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07835-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07835-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07835-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>一款手表的精致感和高级感，除了材质设计，往往还来源于表盘。SUMMIT 2+ 内置了多款万宝龙转数表盘，比如经典的 1858 系列、Boheme 系列、Summit 系列等，很适合西装革履地出席正式场合时换用。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380724" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07792.jpg" alt="" width="5701" height="3801" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07792.jpg 5701w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07792-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07792-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07792-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5701px) 100vw, 5701px" /></p>
<p>还有一些城市系列、运动系列的表盘，更年轻运动，适合日常生活中换用。另外内置的「小问表盘」应用，还可以在线下载更多表盘，保持手表的新鲜感。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380725" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07832.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07832.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07832-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07832-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07832-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>续航方面，SUMMIT 2+ 免不了一天一充。我在中度使用 6 小时后，电量从 100% 掉至 61%。用附赠的充电底座，大约两小时可以将电量从 0% 充至 100%。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380727" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/asjkdb.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/asjkdb.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/asjkdb-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/asjkdb-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/asjkdb-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>最后来揭晓万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 的售价，国行为 9700 元。之于品牌定位来看，这个售价并不令人惊讶。相比两万多的 LV、泰格豪雅的智能腕表，万宝龙这款表的配置已然是有「性价比」的。<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380729" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07862.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07862.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07862-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07862-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07862-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>对于那些喜欢智能手表的便捷，但又需要频繁出入正式场合的人群来说，或许这款万宝龙 SUMMIT 2+ 可以表明你对潮流的态度：既有坚定的审美标准，也敞开自己对新事物的悦纳。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1380728" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07808.jpg" alt="" width="3936" height="2624" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07808.jpg 3936w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07808-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07808-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/DSC07808-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3936px) 100vw, 3936px" /></p>
